The paper also mentions the use of the network for robotics applications, which falls under the category of robotics, making cs.RO a likely sub-category. Finally, the paper compares its results to state-of-the-art methods in computer vision, which is a common practice in the computer vision and pattern recognition conference (CVPR), making it a likely sub-category as well.
